{"tid":992611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士車長涉強姦女兒案　陪審團裁定7項罪名全部不成立","createTime":"2019-01-23T10:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T13:29:05.000Z","uid":15564,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1c4db8ceca08a7baf4f9d95e37dfdd6fb8ce7f64","tid":992611,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1439519_1_L_20190123132318.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1439519_1_L_20190123132318.jpg&h=b22d0ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陪審團裁定被告7項罪名全部不成立，審訊終結。（港台圖片）<br />\n<br />\n一名巴士車長被控多次非禮和強姦親生女兒，案件在審訊期間，女童日前推翻證供，並作供承認誣陷父親和編造一切指控，陪審團裁定被告7項罪名全部不成立，審訊正式終結。警方在庭外透露，日後將不會就案件申請重審。<br />\n<br />\n女童現年15歲，她報稱父親在2015至2017年期間多次非禮和強姦她。<br />\n<br />\n女童目前與母親和胞弟同住，法官表示，由於女童與家庭關係顯然不和睦，建議警方或律政司向法庭申請保護令，或將女童交由社工跟進。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1439519-20190123.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1439519-20190123.htm&d=zxjdt1ahhBQFz5N%2FyWdJ%2FsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3be70534\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1439519-20190123.htm&h=a84c135a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1439519-20190123.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n再睇返之前個post<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">內褲和陰道內都沾有精液  女童:我用廁紙抹入下體誣陷<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/990379\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/990379</a><br />\n炒登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b7a1d55ad3baf6f66ec53217ef98bb750078d8","tid":992611,"uid":44083,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"15 歲就識屈老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6522e3192a7a5d811dd86c099300f0ba537d6965","tid":992611,"uid":53466,"like":0,"di