n>。案件今(25日)在屯門法院提訊，暫毋須答辯。裁判官押後案件到3月8日再訊，讓控方索取法律意見，期間3人還押。<br />\n<br />\n案中<span style=\"color: red;\">被告依次是42歲男子，以及分别為40歲和65歲的2名女子</span>。控罪指他們於去年10月20日至今年1月16日期間，在屯門一單位串謀妨礙司法公正，即威嚇女童X在庭上作假證供。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據了解，<span style=\"color: red;\">次被告</span>在案發期間探望<span style=\"color: red;\">正被覊押的首被告</span>時，首被告着她帶X離港，而她最終<span style=\"color: red;\">在上述案件開審前帶X返回內地</span>。至於<span style=\"color: red;\">第三被告則被指要求X與辯方律師合作，否則會失去父親</span>。<br />\n<br />\n到底全盛時期嘅連登仔可以炒幾多車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e1afe0cfdbe08381ab44ee234dfe7771b234b8","tid":992611,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"成班on9老妨，玩幼女個件唔駛監，懶好心個d就坐撚晒，抵尻死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b3480faeb20a4a4a243b7460eb4334e146251b","tid":992611,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48e1afe0cfdbe08381ab44ee234dfe7771b234b8","tid":992611,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"成班on9老妨，玩幼女個件唔駛監，懶好心個d就坐撚晒，抵尻死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T13:04:29.000Z","msg":"今次老妨嘅首被告都係個老豆"},{"pid":"18a710bb6b2efd300069ade8fef5ae9f71866c66","tid":992611,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48e1afe0cfdbe08381ab44ee234dfe7771b234b8","tid":992611,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"成班on9老妨，玩幼女個件唔駛監，懶好心個d就坐撚晒，抵尻死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"玩幼女嗰件都要呀，佢就係首被告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27477f2d99c85ffdd72126c49a05fc1106ef7846","tid":992611,"uid":